chennai ungalai anbudan varaverkirathu ( english : chennai welcomes you , with love ) is a 2015 tamil-language drama film , written and directed by maruthu pandian . the film stars an ensemble cast featuring bobby simha , prabhanjayan , saranya and lingaa amongst others . music for the film was composed by the camlin-raja duo and the film opened to mixed reviews in april 2015 .